# Phone Notes Auto-Triage

- At the start of each user request, check `docs/notes/NOTES_FROM_PHONE.md` for unprocessed entries (`- [ ]`).
- If unprocessed entries exist, triage each note into the best destination:
  - `CONCEPT.md` for durable product principles/direction.
  - `TODO` for execution-ready work.
  - `IDEAS_BACKLOG.md` for exploratory or not-yet-ready ideas.
- Mark processed entries as `- [x]` after triaging.
- Keep entries concise, deduplicated, and aligned with project conventions.
- Do not duplicate already-implemented functionality in `TODO`.
- In your response, include a short "Phone notes processed" update listing what was moved.
